  %{---------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | HELLO HTML                                                          |
   | Version: 1.0                                                        |
   | File:               ~/apps/hellopy/hellohtml.sh                     |
   |                                                                     |
   | hellohtml.sh                                                        |
   | ------------------------------------------------------------------- |
   |     a bash script that takes an output name and writes              |
   |     boiler-plate html, css, and javascript code to files.           |
   |     index.html is then opened for preview.                          |
   |                                                                     |
   | Setup:                                                              |
   |                                                                     |
   |    $ mkdir -p ~/apps/hellohtml/new                                  |
   |    $ cd hellohtml (the directory this file is in)                   |
   |    $ cp -r * ~/apps/hellohtml                                       |
   |    $ cd ~/apps/hellohtml                                            |
   |    $ chmod a+x hellohtml.sh                                         |
   |    $ ln -s ~/apps/hellohtml/hellohtml.sh  /usr/local/bin/hellohtml  |
   |    $ echo "PATH=/usr/local/bin/:\${PATH}" >> ~/.bash_profile        |
   |                                                                     |
   | Uninstall:                                                          |
   |                                                                     |
   |    $ rm -r ~/apps/hellohtml                                         |
   |    $ rm /usr/local/bin/hellohtml                                    |
   |                                                                     |
   | Usage:                                                              |
   |                                                                     |
   |    $ hellohtml [outputname]                                         |
   |                                                                     |
   | Examples:                                                           |
   |                                                                     |
   |    $ hellohtml cool                                                 |
   |                                                                     |
   | Public Domain Software -- Free to Use as You Like                   |
   | infinitechill.net - By J. Volmer                                    |
   +---------------------------------------------------------------------%}